  "text": "Specifically, the edges of the graph are generated by ignoring all the robot kinematics. Verification of kinematic feasibility along each edge of the graph is postponed to the planning phase. In doing so, our method enables handling the full parameterization of G ∩ P. Although the idea of delaying IK computation has been independently explored in a recent work [CITATION_1] to construct a manipulation graph, the authors' graph still requires discretizing grasp and placement classes, entailing the same problem of heavy pre-processing.",
